crystalline.guide.utilities.cleansing_potion.title=Cleansing Potion
crystalline.guide.utilities.cleansing_potion=The Cleansing Potion has a chance to cure insanity. Here's how it works: \n\nIf you temporary insanity:\n  50 percent chance: cure temporary insanity\n  50 percent chance: raise player insanity by 10 percent\n\nIf you have permanent insanity:\n  1 percent chance: Cure permanent insanity\n  99 percent chance: Kill the player, and do nothing else.

<<< Rebinding >>>

crystalline.guide.utilities.rebinding.title=Rebinding
crystalline.guide.utilities.rebinding=You can bind a crystal using either of these two options: The Rebinding Reagent or Life Crystal Binding
crystalline.guide.utilities.rebinding.life_crystal_binding=You can simply craft a life crystal with another crystal that has binding.
crystalline.guide.utilities.rebinding.rebinding_reagent=You can simply craft a Rebinding Reagent, and right click it, then craft the bound Rebinding Reagent with a crystal.

<<< Restoration >>>

crystalline.guide.utilities.restoration.title=Restoration
crystalline.guide.utilities.restoration=You can restore or create new crystals using the Restoration Apparatus. Simply right click with a crystal to put that in, then put an essence bottle in. You can right-click to get the essence bottle out, and right-click while sneaking to get the crystal out.

