crystalline.guide.utilities.distillation.title=Distillation
crystalline.guide.utilities.distillation=You can create essence bottles by putting items in the Distillation Basin. Simply right-click with an item to put it in, and right click with an empty item to take it out. See Distillation Recipes for recipes.

